00:04:10,703 --> 00:04:15,675
and the new video features is on track to hit $16.99.

69
00:04:16,413 --> 00:04:19,670
Do the math with me. From 2014 to 2021,

70
00:04:20,263 --> 00:04:23,953
the price never moved. From 2023 to 2026,

71
00:04:24,113 --> 00:04:28,300
the price went up 4 times. You are now paying 50% more

72
00:04:28,509 --> 00:04:31,652
for Spotify than you were 3 years ago. 50%!

