00:05:27,653 --> 00:05:31,185
Spotify's profit margin which went from negative in 2022

88
00:05:31,394 --> 00:05:35,166
to over a b— billion dollars in 2024. And Daniel

89
00:05:35,247 --> 00:05:38,345
Ek's bank account, which we'll get to at the end. Right now,

